BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

    [``
\begin{aligned}
   [$question]
      &= [$s1] \\
      &= [$s2] \\
      &= [$s3] \\
      &= [$s4] \\
      &= [$s5]
\end{aligned}
    ``]

The correct answer is [$pop->correct_ans()].

END_PGML_SOLUTION

